data.description: Indulge in luxury living with this exquisite 6-bed, 4-bath estate nestled on over 1 acre of pristine country/coastal beauty. Spanning 4,458 sqft, this residence offers unparalleled sophistication. Experience opulent renovations, including a remodeled kitchen, added bedroom/bathroom, and new exterior doors. Revel in the 75ft Olympic-size lap pool with a sun shelf and gas heater. The property is a haven, fully fenced with a coded, solar-powered automatic gated entry leading to a circle driveway with parking for twenty. A new Generac natural gas whole-home generator ensures uninterrupted comfort. The detached three-car garage adds to the allure of this extraordinary home.
